  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 11th level, once per long rest, when a creature would succeed on their saving throw, but not critically succeed their saving throw against a Genjutsu you cast, you can force them to suffer the effects of a failure. </p><p>Starting at 15th level you may use this ability once per short rest. </p><p>Finally, beginning at 20th level, when you would use this feature they instead suffer the effects of a critical failure, if the jutsu cast has such a failure condition.</p>",
